story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0100:
Morning, everyone! Guess what? We finally
found Team Rocket’s hideout!
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0200:
Really? That’s amazing, Blue! When did you
find it?
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0300:
Blaine, Lorelei, and I did a bit more searching
last night.
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0400: And now it’s time for a showdown!
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0500:
Brock and Sabrina are on their way to help.
This time, we’re going on the offensive!
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0700:
Erika and Misty will be helping us out, too! They’ll
take the side opposite of ours.
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0800: We’re about to infiltrate an enemy hideout...
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_0900:
It’s gonna be pretty dangerous. Think you can
handle it?
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_1800: Paulo! I’m so glad you came!
story_teamrocket_01_09000/2401_1201_1900: All right, it’s showtime! Game faces on!
